<plot>This light hearted musical series features family entertainer Eric Nagler as a musician and single parent living in a trailer park with his pre-teen daughter Kaley, who wants to be a dancer. Other regulars in this small friendly community are C.J. a mischievous life-size puppet who is Eric's manager-in-training, young Max, Eric's biggest fan and critic, and Max's mother Andrea; Kaley's best friend, Prue, and Marian, a librarian with a taste for adventure. Celebrated guests turn up to perform with Eric and the gang.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?180395</url></doc>
